OL,3,CFame reduces a celebrity's life
OL,4,Cexpectancy by nearly five years, study
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe research team also point out that
OL,8,Fsolo artists appeared to carry a
OL,9,Fhigher risk of early death, when
OL,10,Fcompared to singers in a band.
OL,12,F"Possible explanations for this
OL,13,Finclude increased individual exposure
OL,14,Fto the public with the accompanying
OL,15,Fhigher emotional strain," they said.
OL,17,F"Being in a band may offer emotional
OL,18,Fand practical support, while solo
OL,19,Fartists may face more isolation and
OL,20,Fstress."
